{"tid":2445283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家指政府有意採購第 4 款疫苗　採重組蛋白技術　料為「美國 Novavax」或「成都威斯克」","createTime":"2021-03-13T13:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T00:28:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"32d509be7929659e23d71026708392560f8238ff","tid":2445283,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"港府現時已採購 3 款疫苗，分別為科興、BioNTech 及牛津大學／阿斯利康。衞生防護中心疫苗可預防疾病科學委員會主席劉宇隆向《立場新聞》透露，政府有意採購第 4 種技術平台，相信會是「重組蛋白技術」，有機會採購美國生物科技公司 Novavax，或成都威斯克生物醫藥有限公司研發的疫苗，但最終結果仍須待政府公布。醫院藥劑師學會會長崔俊明亦指，政府有意採購 Novavax，但認為強生藥廠的疫苗數據較充足，但因所用技術與阿斯利康疫苗一樣，不符政府不同技術平台的要求，故沒有被選中，呼籲政府可以考慮強生疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%AC%AC-4-%E6%AC%BE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E6%8E%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93-%E6%96%99%E7%82%BA-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-novavax-%E6%88%96-%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E5%A8%81%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%25AC%25AC-4-%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E6%258E%25A1%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%259B%258B%25E7%2599%25BD%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B-novavax-%25E6%2588%2596-%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2585%258B%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=feb46d5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%25AC%25AC-4-%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E6%258E%25A1%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%259B%258B%25E7%2599%25BD%25E6%2